ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;When I was young I was a communist, then an anarchist and finally a libertarian before coming to be an eco-facist.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"bf5cfb704751bc1fa6843e0157c90d2947b5edc4","tid":1062673,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:24:07.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4938de77ed7a6d41dce1fa740973fe861450dd","tid":1062673,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21819e79f1d929511ad5e581288f804ad53d88c9","tid":1062673,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190315/59371177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59371177&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=304c5190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59371177&h=8c17fa12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190315/59371177</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭基督城今日發生恐怖槍擊案，槍手闖入兩間清真寺向正在禱告的穆斯林掃射，目前已造成至少40人死亡。據新西蘭媒體報道，其中一名槍手是28歲澳洲出生的白人男子Brenton Tarrant。<span style=\"color: red;\">他在今年1月21日曾在網上發表一份長達70頁的宣言，並聲稱世上與他政治及社會價值最相近的國家就是中國。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrenton這份宣言題為《大清洗--邁向新社會》，以問答形式撰寫，當中詳述他的個人理念，以及解釋為何他要發動這次滅絕人性的襲擊，昨日曾更新過一次。<br />\n<br />\nBrenton承認，他的所作所為是恐怖主義活動，並指自己是在打擊那些有高生育率並且想佔據歐洲的「入侵者」，特別是穆斯林新移民，又提及「聖殿騎士團」、「十字軍」，還坦言澳洲及新西蘭是歐洲的一部份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，他並沒有承認自己是左翼還是右翼份子，並稱這視乎人們如何作出定義，但他覺得自己傾向社會主義。至於他是否法西斯主義者，Brenton這樣說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">與我的政治及社會價值最相近的國家，就是中華人民共和國。（The nation with the closest political and social values to my own is the People&rsquo;s Republic of China）</span>」<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n支持槍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對槍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"做得好，臨死都過中國一棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaee12f8230a77a71a245ae1eb5ddc04b2af10a","tid":1062673,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"backup<br />\nNYT舊ver<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-gb/news/uknews/christchurch-shooting-updates-49-are-dead-after-2-mosques-are-hit/ar-BBUNI60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fen-gb%2Fnews%2Fuknews%2Fchristchurch-shooting-updates-49-are-dead-after-2-mosques-are-hit%2Far-BBUNI60&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ff83a4ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/en-gb/news/uknews/christchurch-shooting-updates-49-are-dead-after-2-mosques-are-hit/ar-BBUNI60</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>In his manifesto, he identified himself as a 28-year-old man born in Australia and listed his white nationalist heroes. <br />\n<br />\nHe described what he said had motivated him to carry out the attack, and said he had purposely used guns to stir discord in the United States over the Second Amendment&rsquo;s provision on the right to bear arms.<br />\n<br />\nHe also declared himself a fascist. &ldquo;For once, the person that will be called a fascist, is an actual fascist,&rdquo; he wrote in the manifesto, adding that China&rsquo;s &ldquo;political and social values&rdquo; were closest to his own. </blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNYT新ver<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/14/world/asia/new-zealand-shooting-updates-christchurch.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fnew-zealand-shooting-updates-christchurch.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=345b5f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/14/world/asia/new-zealand-shooting-updates-christchurch.html</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nIn his manifesto, he identified himself as a 28-year-old man born in Australia and listed his white nationalist heroes.<br />\n<br />\nWriting that he had purposely used guns to stir discord in the United States over the Second Amendment&rsquo;s provision on the right to bear arms, he also declared himself a fascist. &ldquo;For once, the person that will be called a fascist, is an actual fascist,&rdquo; he wrote.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d729ce71c407663d4d48167c98635f092f83e388","tid":1062673,"uid":36162,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0e451836d6b90b2b9bef3a95165fc0063351585b","tid":1062673,"uid":242301,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"dddec505f621486d593f1ba900de3210e20c6641","tid":1062673,"uid":36162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06a07a82953696254c75fcdc982da35432a41f5","tid":1062673,"uid":143499,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEqLkox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEqLkox.jpg&h=7d6eaf82&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"事實上係中國佔領新彊，個情况同佢見到嘅新西蘭完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"咁澳洲新西蘭白人宜家重有無迫害當地土著?"},{"pid":"893cc327a3bc342e99121191009e6998fbf7daba","tid":1062673,"uid":51121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8b10013db08a9f6de27193d6869c2144a53d0d37","tid":1062673,"uid":103922,"like":92,"dislike":3,"score":89,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔支持槍手，原來連登仔價值觀同中國最接近<img src=\"/assets/faces